{"data":[{"name":"74:1","price":"ಓ ಹೊದಿಕೆಯನ್ನು ಹೊದ್ದುಕೊಂಡವರೇ![1]","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡمُدَّثِّرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5496,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1] ಪ್ರವಾದಿಯವರಿಗೆ (ಅವರ ಮೇಲೆ ಅಲ್ಲಾಹನ ಕೃಪೆ ಮತ್ತು ಶಾಂತಿಯಿರಲಿ) ಮೊಟ್ಟಮೊದಲು ಸೂರ ಅಲಕ್‌ನ ಪ್ರಥಮ 5 ವಚನಗಳು ಅವತೀರ್ಣವಾದವು. ನಂತರ ದೀರ್ಘ ಸಮಯದ ತನಕ ಅವರಿಗೆ ಕುರ್‌ಆನ್ ಅವತೀರ್ಣವಾಗಲಿಲ್ಲ. ಒಂದಿನ ಇದ್ದಕ್ಕಿದ್ದಂತೆ ಹಿರಾ ಗುಹೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ನೋಡಿದ ಅದೇ ದೇವದೂತರು ಆಕಾಶ ಮತ್ತು ಭೂಮಿಯ ಮಧ್ಯೆ ಸಂಪೂರ್ಣ ದಿಗಂತವನ್ನು ಮುಚ್ಚುವ ರೀತಿಯಲ್ಲಿ ಕುಳಿತಿರುವುದನ್ನು ಕಂಡರು. ಅವರು ಭಯದಿಂದ ಮನೆಗೆ ಓಡಿ ನನ್ನನ್ನು ಹೊದಿಯಿರಿ; ನನ್ನನ್ನು ಹೊದಿಯಿರಿ ಎಂದರು. ಅವರನ್ನು ಹೊದಿಕೆಯಿಂದ ಹೊದಿಯಲಾಯಿತು. ಆಗ ಈ ವಚನಗಳು ಅವತೀರ್ಣವಾದವು.","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"yāayyuhā al-mudathiru ","translations":["O you","who covers himself","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["yāayyuhā","al-mudathiru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2960],[2,2960,4745]]}},{"name":"74:2","price":"ಎದ್ದೇಳಿರಿ ಮತ್ತು ಎಚ್ಚರಿಕೆ ನೀಡಿರಿ.","arabic":"قُمۡ فَأَنذِرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5497,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"qum fa-andhir ","translations":["Stand up","and warn","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["qum","fa-andhir",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2765]]}},{"name":"74:3","price":"ನಿಮ್ಮ ಪರಿಪಾಲಕನ (ಅಲ್ಲಾಹನ) ಮಹಾತ್ಮೆಯನ್ನು ಕೊಂಡಾಡಿರಿ.","arabic":"وَرَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5498,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"warabbaka fakabbir ","translations":["And your Lord","magnify","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["warabbaka","fakabbir",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,2275]]}},{"name":"74:4","price":"ನಿಮ್ಮ ಬಟ್ಟೆಗಳನ್ನು ಶುದ್ಧವಾಗಿಡಿರಿ.","arabic":"وَثِيَابَكَ فَطَهِّرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5499,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"wathiyābaka faṭahhir ","translations":["And your clothing","purify","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wathiyābaka","faṭahhir",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,2615]]}},{"name":"74:5","price":"ಅಶುದ್ಧವನ್ನು ವರ್ಜಿಸಿರಿ.","arabic":"وَٱلرُّجۡزَ فَٱهۡجُرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5500,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ruj'za fa-uh'jur ","translations":["And uncleanliness","avoid","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ruj'za","fa-uh'jur",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,990],[2,990,2145]]}},{"name":"74:6","price":"ಉಪಕಾರ ಮಾಡಿ ಹೆಚ್ಚು ಗಳಿಸುವ ವ್ಯಾಮೋಹ ಬಿಟ್ಟುಬಿಡಿ.","arabic":"وَلَا تَمۡنُن تَسۡتَكۡثِرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5501,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"walā tamnun tastakthiru ","translations":["And (do) not","confer favor","(to) acquire more","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","tamnun","tastakthiru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1740],[3,1740,3655]]}},{"name":"74:7","price":"ನಿಮ್ಮ ಪರಿಪಾಲಕನ (ಅಲ್ಲಾಹನ) ಮಾರ್ಗದಲ್ಲಿ ತಾಳ್ಮೆಯಿಂದಿರಿ.","arabic":"وَلِرَبِّكَ فَٱصۡبِرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5502,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"walirabbika fa-iṣ'bir ","translations":["And for your Lord","be patient","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["walirabbika","fa-iṣ'bir",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,2395]]}},{"name":"74:8","price":"ಕಹಳೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಊದಲಾಗುವಾಗ.","arabic":"فَإِذَا نُقِرَ فِي ٱلنَّاقُورِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5503,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā nuqira fī al-nāqūri ","translations":["Then when","is blown","in","the trumpet","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","nuqira","fī","al-nāqūri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1370],[3,1370,1560],[4,1560,5845]]}},{"name":"74:9","price":"ಆ ದಿನವು ಅತ್ಯಂತ ಕಠಿಣ ದಿನವಾಗಿರುವುದು.","arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ يَوۡمَئِذٖ يَوۡمٌ عَسِيرٌ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5504,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhālika yawma-idhin yawmun ʿasīrun ","translations":["That","Day","(will be) a Day","difficult","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhālika","yawma-idhin","yawmun","ʿasīrun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,2740],[3,2740,3390],[4,3390,6275]]}},{"name":"74:10","price":"ಅದು ಸತ್ಯನಿಷೇಧಿಗಳಿಗೆ ಸುಗಮವಾಗಿರುವುದಿಲ್ಲ.","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡكَٰفِرِينَ غَيۡرُ يَسِيرٖ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5505,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā al-kāfirīna ghayru yasīrin ","translations":["For","the disbelievers ","not","easy","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","al-kāfirīna","ghayru","yasīrin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1840],[3,1840,2390],[4,2390,5605]]}},{"name":"74:11","price":"ನನ್ನನ್ನು ಹಾಗೂ ನಾನು ಏಕಾಂಗಿಯಾಗಿ ಸೃಷ್ಟಿದವನನ್ನು ಬಿಟ್ಟುಬಿಡಿ.[1]","arabic":"ذَرۡنِي وَمَنۡ خَلَقۡتُ وَحِيدٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5506,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1] ಅಂದರೆ ಅವನ ವಿಷಯವನ್ನು ನಾನು ನೋಡಿಕೊಳ್ಳುವೆನು. ಅವನು ಅವನ ತಾಯಿಯ ಹೊಟ್ಟೆಯಿಂದ ಹೊರಬರುವಾಗ ಅವನಲ್ಲಿ ಐಶ್ವರ್ಯ ಅಥವಾ ಮಕ್ಕಳಿರಲಿಲ್ಲ. ಇವೆಲ್ಲವೂ ನಾನು ಅವನಿಗೆ ನೀಡಿದ ಅನುಗ್ರಹಗಳು. ಆದರೂ ಅವನು ಈಗ ನನ್ನ ವಿರುದ್ಧ ಸೆಟೆದು ನಿಂತಿದ್ದಾನೆ. — ಇಲ್ಲಿ ಹೇಳಲಾಗಿರುವುದು ಕುರೈಷಿ ಮುಖಂಡ ವಲೀದ್ ಬಿನ್ ಮುಗೀರ ಎಂಬವನ ಬಗ್ಗೆಯಾಗಿದೆ.","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"dharnī waman khalaqtu waḥīdan ","translations":["Leave Me","and whom","I created","alone","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["dharnī","waman","khalaqtu","waḥīdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,1460],[3,1460,2360],[4,2360,3595]]}},{"name":"74:12","price":"ನಾನು ಅವನಿಗೆ ಹೇರಳ ಐಶ್ವರ್ಯವನ್ನು ನೀಡಿದೆನು.","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡتُ لَهُۥ مَالٗا مَّمۡدُودٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5507,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"wajaʿaltu lahu mālan mamdūdan ","translations":["And I granted","to him","wealth","extensive","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wajaʿaltu","lahu","mālan","mamdūdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,1520],[3,1520,2180],[4,2180,4145]]}},{"name":"74:13","price":"ಸನ್ನದ್ಧರಾಗಿರುವ ಗಂಡು ಮಕ್ಕಳನ್ನು ನೀಡಿದೆನು.","arabic":"وَبَنِينَ شُهُودٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5508,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"wabanīna shuhūdan ","translations":["And children","present","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wabanīna","shuhūdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,950],[2,950,2255]]}},{"name":"74:14","price":"ನಾನು ಅವನಿಗೆ ಅನೇಕ ಅನುಕೂಲತೆಗಳನ್ನು ಮಾಡಿಕೊಟ್ಟೆನು.","arabic":"وَمَهَّدتُّ لَهُۥ تَمۡهِيدٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5509,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"wamahhadttu lahu tamhīdan ","translations":["And I spread","for him","ease","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wamahhadttu","lahu","tamhīdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1700],[3,1700,3165]]}},{"name":"74:15","price":"ಆದರೂ ನಾನು ಅವನಿಗೆ ಇನ್ನೂ ಹೆಚ್ಚು ನೀಡಬೇಕೆಂದು ಅವನು ಹಾತೊರೆಯುತ್ತಾನೆ.","arabic":"ثُمَّ يَطۡمَعُ أَنۡ أَزِيدَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5510,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma yaṭmaʿu an azīda ","translations":["Then","he desires","that","I (should) add more","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","yaṭmaʿu","an","azīda",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1110],[2,1110,1910],[3,1910,2260],[4,2260,5165]]}},{"name":"74:16","price":"ಖಂಡಿತ ಇಲ್ಲ. ಅವನು ನಮ್ಮ ವಚನಗಳ ವಿರೋಧಿಯಾಗಿದ್ದಾನೆ.","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ لِأٓيَٰتِنَا عَنِيدٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5511,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahu kāna liāyātinā ʿanīdan ","translations":["By no means","Indeed, he","has been","to Our Verses","stubborn","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahu","kāna","liāyātinā","ʿanīdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,2920],[3,2920,3520],[4,3520,5140],[5,5140,6355]]}},{"name":"74:17","price":"ಸದ್ಯವೇ ನಾನು ಅವನನ್ನು ಒಂದು ಪ್ರಯಾಸಕರ ಏರುವಿಕೆಯನ್ನು ಏರುವಂತೆ ಮಾಡುವೆನು.[1]","arabic":"سَأُرۡهِقُهُۥ صَعُودًا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5512,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1] ಅಂದರೆ ಅವನಿಗೆ ಸಹಿಸಲು ಅಸಾಧ್ಯವಾದ ಶಿಕ್ಷೆಯನ್ನು ನೀಡುವೆನು. ಇತರ ಕೆಲವು ವ್ಯಾಖ್ಯಾನಕಾರರು ಹೇಳುವಂತೆ ನರಕದಲ್ಲಿ ಒಂದು ಅಗ್ನಿಯ ಪರ್ವತವಿದ್ದು ಈತ ಅದನ್ನು ಏರುತ್ತಲೇ ಇರುವನು.","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"sa-ur'hiquhu ṣaʿūdan ","translations":["Soon I will cover Him","(with) a laborious punishment","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["sa-ur'hiquhu","ṣaʿūdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,2925]]}},{"name":"74:18","price":"ಅವನು ಯೋಚಿಸಿದನು ಮತ್ತು ನಿರ್ಣಯಿಸಿದನು.","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ فَكَّرَ وَقَدَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5513,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu fakkara waqaddara ","translations":["Indeed, he","thought","and plotted","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","fakkara","waqaddara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1270],[2,1270,2110],[3,2110,3315]]}},{"name":"74:19","price":"ಅವನು ನಾಶವಾಗಲಿ! ಅವನು ಹೇಗೆ ನಿರ್ಣಯಿಸಿದನು?","arabic":"فَقُتِلَ كَيۡفَ قَدَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5514,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"faqutila kayfa qaddara ","translations":["So may he be destroyed","how","he plotted","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["faqutila","kayfa","qaddara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1420],[3,1420,2445]]}},{"name":"74:20","price":"ಪುನಃ ಅವನು ನಾಶವಾಗಲಿ! ಅವನು ಹೇಗೆ ನಿರ್ಣಯಿಸಿದನು?","arabic":"ثُمَّ قُتِلَ كَيۡفَ قَدَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5515,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma qutila kayfa qaddara ","translations":["Then","may he be destroyed","how","he plotted","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","qutila","kayfa","qaddara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1250],[2,1250,1910],[3,1910,2470],[4,2470,3625]]}},{"name":"74:21","price":"ನಂತರ ಅವನು ನೋಡಿದನು.","arabic":"ثُمَّ نَظَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5516,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma naẓara ","translations":["Then","he looked","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","naẓara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,2305]]}},{"name":"74:22","price":"ನಂತರ ಅವನು ಹುಬ್ಬುಗಂಟಿಕ್ಕಿದನು ಮತ್ತು ಮುಖವನ್ನು ಸಿಂಡರಿಸಿದನು.","arabic":"ثُمَّ عَبَسَ وَبَسَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5517,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma ʿabasa wabasara ","translations":["Then","he frowned","and scowled","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","ʿabasa","wabasara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1370],[2,1370,2080],[3,2080,3175]]}},{"name":"74:23","price":"ನಂತರ ಅವನು ಹಿಂದಡಿಯಿಟ್ಟನು ಮತ್ತು ಅಹಂಕಾರ ತೋರಿದನು.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ وَٱسۡتَكۡبَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5518,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma adbara wa-is'takbara ","translations":["Then","he turned back","and was proud","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","adbara","wa-is'takbara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2030],[3,2030,3425]]}},{"name":"74:24","price":"ನಂತರ ಅವನು ಹೇಳಿದನು: “ಇದು (ಕುರ್‌ಆನ್) ನಕಲು ಮಾಡಲಾದ ಮಾಟಗಾರಿಕೆಯಲ್ಲದೆ ಇನ್ನೇನೂ ಅಲ್ಲ.","arabic":"فَقَالَ إِنۡ هَٰذَآ إِلَّا سِحۡرٞ يُؤۡثَرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5519,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"faqāla in hādhā illā siḥ'run yu'tharu ","translations":["Then he said","Not","(is) this","but","magic","imitated","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["faqāla","in","h